# 🪙 Prosper Gold — Crypto Investment Simulator

**Prosper Gold** is a modern web app that simulates cryptocurrency trading and investment management.  
It lets users register, log in, view live crypto prices, and perform simulated buy/sell trades in real time.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 **User Authentication** – Register and log in securely  
- 💰 **Simulated Trading** – Buy and sell virtual crypto assets  
- 📊 **Live Price Feed** – View real-time cryptocurrency prices  
- 💼 **Portfolio Tracking** – Monitor your assets and trades  
- 🌐 **Responsive Design** – Works smoothly on mobile and desktop  

---

## 🧱 Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology Used |
|--------|----------------|
| Frontend | HTML, CSS, JavaScript |
| Backend | C++ (with FastCGI or REST server) |
| Database | PostgreSQL / SQLite |
| Deployment | Render.com / Netlify |

